data.name: coverNeedsContent.Text
data.value:
All your work safe and private.

MyGIS has developed special algorithm and database infrastructure to guarantee security and privacy.

Most users fear of accidental loss of data. MyGIS ensures data integrity and versioning. This means that even if you delete or change a data layer, there is always instant roll-back.

Developing data layers for public use, or using sensitive personal/corporate information, you MyGIS offers you easy and efficient control on what you keep off-site, what you share with certain users and what you share with the public.

data.name: whatIsContent.Text
data.value:
Mapping just got easier

MyGIS is basically your GIS. It is a free service that lets you bring all your data on a map. This means that almost any source of information (e.g. client databases, city plans, even moving vehicles) can be geocoded and plotted on your map. Additional information such as photos, videos, city plans are also easily georeferenced and included within your maps. This means that you can have instant access to your portfolio, anytime, anywhere.

MyGIS also makes sharing data with others, whether you're a student or professional, civil servant or citizen. You may browse through thousands of data layers shared by others, choose according to your needs and make your map in a few minutes. On the other hand, you may produce data layers and decide to share them for free, or make a profit applying a reasonable fee.
